                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18450616-1338-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18450616-1338-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18450616-1338-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18450616-cd-38" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18450616-1338-offence-1 t18450616-cd-38"></join>24th of May</rs>, 2 puncheons, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18450616-name-547" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450616-name-547" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450616-name-547" type="surname" value="HESSE"></interp>
