                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's' former conviction, from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted, 10th May, 1841, of larceny, as servant; confined four months.</hi>)</p>
